125
00:15:27,340 --> 00:15:28,300
Because you're here.

126
00:15:28,900 --> 00:15:29,780
I come here for you.

127
00:15:31,020 --> 00:15:31,740
For me?

128
00:15:36,420 --> 00:15:38,220
