130
00:15:40,020 --> 00:15:40,860
My Ji Heng?

131
00:15:42,340 --> 00:15:43,380
Why do you think so?

132
00:15:46,220 --> 00:15:47,740
Because I have remembered everything.

133
00:15:50,020 --> 00:15:51,020
I've remembered

134
00:15:52,820 --> 00:15:53,780
how hard

135
00:15:54,580 --> 00:15:56,900
I tried to find pimpon fruit earlier.

136
00:15:58,620 --> 00:16:01,060
You gave it to her

137
00:16:01,620 --> 00:16:03,100
as soon as she asked.

138
00:16:05,220 --> 00:16:07,460
If you hadn't fallen for Ji Heng and wanted to flatter her,

139
00:16:08,500 --> 00:16:10,700
