148
00:16:35,940 --> 00:16:37,860
wasn't well planned by you at the first place.

149
00:16:39,020 --> 00:16:41,500
It's because you never intended to give me,

150
00:16:41,660 --> 00:16:42,980
and you gave it to her without a hitch.

151
00:16:50,020 --> 00:16:51,340
Why didn't you want to give it to me?

152
00:16:54,980 --> 00:16:56,020
Because

153
00:16:58,220 --> 00:17:00,060
I thought you would make a cake

154
00:17:00,460 --> 00:17:02,300
with pimpon fruit for Yan Chiwu.

155
00:17:03,660 --> 00:17:04,660
