160
00:17:18,860 --> 00:17:20,220
Are you still mad at me?

161
00:17:21,220 --> 00:17:21,980
What can I do

162
00:17:22,300 --> 00:17:24,140
to make you believe that I like you, Xiaobai?

163
00:17:26,420 --> 00:17:27,420
What do you want me to do?

164
00:17:30,500 --> 00:17:32,860
Will giving my heart to you work?

165
00:17:39,580 --> 00:17:40,540
If I hadn't liked you,

166
00:17:42,140 --> 00:17:43,980
