167
00:17:47,100 --> 00:17:47,660
Your Majesty.

168
00:17:48,180 --> 00:17:49,020
I've already known

169
00:17:49,260 --> 00:17:50,740
what you've done for me, Xiaobai.

170
00:18:02,940 --> 00:18:03,940
You're bleeding again.

171
00:18:06,620 --> 00:18:07,140
It doesn't matter.

172
00:18:10,580 --> 00:18:12,580
When the banshee attacked you,

173
00:18:12,700 --> 00:18:13,780
why didn't you dodge?

174
00:18:14,060 --> 00:18:15,340
And you made yourself hurt.

175
00:18:17,420 --> 00:18:18,420
What are you saying?

176
00:18:19,740 --> 00:18:20,660
I can't hear you.

177
00:18:21,420 --> 00:18:23,180
You can hear me clearly.

178
00:18:25,540 --> 00:18:26,580
Are you sure

179
00:18:27,580 --> 00:18:28,740
that you want to ask me these

180
