182
00:18:33,580 --> 00:18:34,900
Why not use them?

183
00:18:37,940 --> 00:18:38,980
Maybe

184
00:18:41,140 --> 00:18:43,220
I want to show off my superb kung fu.

185
00:18:47,740 --> 00:18:48,220
Xiaobai,

186
00:18:49,940 --> 00:18:51,060
that you don't talk to me

187
00:18:52,660 --> 00:18:54,940
is because I didn't kiss you well just now,

188
00:18:55,860 --> 00:18:58,420
or I didn't flatter you?

189
00:19:02,580 --> 00:19:03,340
Please excuse me.

190
00:19:04,580 --> 00:19:06,580
I don't have much experience in this aspect,

191
00:19:07,180 --> 00:19:09,140
