201
00:19:42,060 --> 00:19:42,940
There's

202
00:19:43,340 --> 00:19:45,540
something that I can almost recall,

203
00:19:46,620 --> 00:19:48,580
but I don't seem to recall it clearly.

204
00:19:49,260 --> 00:19:50,500
There may be something wrong.

205
00:19:53,020 --> 00:19:53,620
Your Majesty,

206
00:19:56,420 --> 00:19:58,300
