210
00:20:16,500 --> 00:20:17,060
Xiaobai,

211
00:20:18,180 --> 00:20:19,540
there's too much misunderstanding between us.

212
00:20:21,220 --> 00:20:23,020
Dream of Aranya is bizarre and motley.

213
00:20:24,180 --> 00:20:25,980
And your primordial spirit just came back to your own body.

214
00:20:26,500 --> 00:20:27,860
