We shouldn't talk here for too long.

218
00:20:38,060 --> 00:20:39,740
When we leave the Dream of Aranya,

219
00:20:40,740 --> 00:20:44,460
I'll tell you the truth to clear up
all the misunderstandings on your mind.

220
00:20:46,900 --> 00:20:47,460
Xiaobai,

221
00:20:49,180 --> 00:20:50,660
you have no idea why you're here.

222
00:20:51,020 --> 00:20:52,420
It's because you were hurt heavily.

223
00:20:53,340 --> 00:20:55,180
I nursed your health with my blood for a long time.

224
00:20:56,060 --> 00:20:57,300
To make you recover soon,

225
00:20:58,020 --> 00:21:00,260
I led you to the Dream of Aranya for recuperation.

226
00:21:01,860 --> 00:21:02,780
I didn't lie to you.

227
00:21:04,140 --> 00:21:05,260
I came here for you.

228
00:21:06,500 --> 00:21:09,220
In the Dream of Aranya, I'm Xi Ze,

229
00:21:09,580 --> 00:21:10,580
and you're Aranya.

230
00:21:11,540 --> 00:21:12,980
We're supposed to be a couple.

231
00:21:16,340 --> 00:21:17,460
I'll definitely protect you.

232
00:21:17,980 --> 00:21:19,060
When everything comes to an end,

233
00:21:20,140 --> 00:21:21,780
I'll tell you the truth in person.

234
00:21:23,460 --> 00:21:24,580
You're Xi Ze,

235
00:21:25,180 --> 00:21:26,300
and we are married.

236
00:21:28,180 --> 00:21:29,660
You took me to see Yueling flowers,

237
00:21:30,340 --> 00:21:31,620
and sang a song for me.

238
00:21:35,020 --> 00:21:37,220
I remembered. I remembered it all.

239
00:21:40,220 --> 00:21:43,340
Then sing one more for me.

240
00:21:44,180 --> 00:21:45,020
Why should I?

241
00:21:47,580 --> 00:21:49,900
I feel too painful to fall asleep.

242
00:21:58,020 --> 00:21:59,940
If such a brave person says it hurts,

243
00:22:00,260 --> 00:22:01,220
he must be badly hurt.

244
00:22:05,260 --> 00:22:05,660
Come here.

245
00:22:10,460 --> 00:22:10,980
Sing it.

246
00:22:14,180 --> 00:22:17,780
Yueling flowers, the snow in the sky.

247
