252
00:22:39,180 --> 00:22:42,180
Yueling flowers don't know

253
00:22:42,780 --> 00:22:46,300
they never meet the moon.

254
00:22:46,940 --> 00:22:49,780
They bloom in an instant.

255
00:22:50,220 --> 00:22:54,260
They wither in an instant.

256
00:22:54,500 --> 00:23:01,020
The instants witness their blooming and withering.

257
00:23:04,020 --> 00:23:05,220
They wither when the moon comes out.

258
00:23:05,980 --> 00:23:07,220
They bloom when the moon disappears.

259
00:23:08,580 --> 00:23:09,060
Xiaobai,

260
00:23:10,740 --> 00:23:12,780
I won't hurt your feelings anymore.

261
00:23:16,020 --> 00:23:17,860
You still remember what I said that night.

262
00:23:18,780 --> 00:23:20,540
More than what you said that night.

263
00:23:23,100 --> 00:23:25,580
I also heard a song when I was a child,

264
00:23:25,980 --> 00:23:27,020
which was different from what you sang.

265
00:23:27,260 --> 00:23:28,380
Let me sing it for you.

266
00:23:29,580 --> 00:23:30,660
