267
00:23:33,540 --> 00:23:37,500
When a full moon night comes,

268
00:23:37,980 --> 00:23:41,340
Moonlight shines on the mountain.

269
00:23:41,660 --> 00:23:45,300
Down the mountain stands a short fence.

270
00:23:45,700 --> 00:23:49,300
